<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Du'ā – Du'ā al-Safar (Clear Arabic)</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Amiri:wght@400;700&family=Lateef&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: #faf7f2;
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    color: #2c2c2c;
    padding: 0 0 80px;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .header {
    background: #1a3d26;
    color: #f5e6c8;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .header h1 { font-family: 'Amiri', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .header p  { font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* ── Section Labels ── */
  .section-label {
    text-align: center;
    background: #ede8df;
    color: #7a5c3a;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 8px;
    margin: 20px 16px 5px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ── Verse block ── */
  .verse-block {
    background: #fff;
    margin: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border: 1px solid #e0d8cc;
  }

  /* ── Optimized Arabic Text ── */
  .arabic-display {
    direction: rtl;
    font-family: 'Lateef', cursive;
    font-size: 2.2rem; /* Increased size for clarity */
    line-height: 1.8;   /* Extra height for vowels */
    color: #111;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    word-spacing: 4px;
  }

  .transliteration {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #555;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 15px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid #f0ede9;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .translation {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #3d2a1a;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #c9b99a, transparent);
    margin: 25px 40px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <h1>دُعَاءُ السَّفَر</h1>
  <p>The Traveler's Supplication</p>
</div>

<div class="section-label">Opening</div>

<div class="verse-block">
  <div class="arabic-display">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ</div>
  <div class="transliteration">(Bismillāh) ×3</div>
  <div class="translation">In the name of Allah</div>
</div>

<div class="verse-block">
  <div class="arabic-display">الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ</div>
  <div class="transliteration">Al-ḥamdulillāh</div>
  <div class="translation">All praise is due to Allah</div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">The Quranic Supplication</div>

<div class="verse-block">
  <div class="arabic-display">
    سُبْحَانَ الَّذِي سَخَّرَ لَنَا هَٰذَا وَمَا كُنَّا لَهُ مُقْرِنِينَ
  </div>
  <div class="arabic-display" style="font-size: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;">
    وَإِنَّا إِلَىٰ رَبِّنَا لَمُنقَلِبُونَ
  </div>
  <div class="transliteration">Subḥān-alladhī sakh-khara lanā hadhā wa mā kunnā lahu muqrinīn. Wa innā ilā Rabbinā lamunqalibūn.</div>
  <div class="translation">Glory be to the One who has subjected this to us, and we could not have otherwise subdued it. And indeed, to our Lord we are returning.</div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">Praise &amp; Repentance</div>

<div class="verse-block">
  <div class="transliteration">Al-ḥamdulillāh (×3) &amp; Allāhu Akbar (×3)</div>
</div>

<div class="verse-block">
  <div class="arabic-display">
    سُبْحَانَكَ إِنِّي ظَلَمْتُ نَفْسِي فَاغْفِرْ لِي فَإِنَّهُ لَا يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ
  </div>
  <div class="transliteration">Subḥānaka innī ẓalamtu nafsī faghfir-lī fa-innahu lā yaghfiru-dhunūba illā Ant.</div>
  <div class="translation">Glory is to You, indeed I have wronged myself, so forgive me, for indeed none forgives sins except You.</div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

</body>
</html>
